==Education==
Fox Glacier School is a coeducational full primary (years 1-8) school with a [[Socio-Economic Decile|decile rating]] of 8 and a roll of 17.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tki.org.nz/e/schools/display_school_info.php?school_id=3342|title=Te Kete Ipurangi - Fox Glacier School|publisher=[[Ministry of Education (New Zealand)|Ministry of Education]]}}</ref> The school started in 1877.<ref>{{cite book|title=Black sands and golden years : Weheka-Fox Glacier School jubilee 1877-1979|year=1979|first=Margaret|last=Hall|publisher=Bascands}}</ref>

